0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:51:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">(請廣傳！）</span><br />\n<br />\n以下餐廳/店舖係曾經係反送中期間，<br />\n強烈譴責示威者係暴徒擾亂香港、支持黑警濫用暴力、想食兩家茶禮既店舖<br />\n希望大家係抗爭以外，平時都可以齊心抵制呢啲舖頭，唔好再幫襯！<br />\n比佢地知支持黑警係要付出代價<br />\n所有資料由連登、Facebook、IG綜合所得，內容包括但不限於餐廳/飲品店/網店/實體店<br />\n如有補充，可以係下面填表 （spreadsheet唔會公開編輯驚比人玩野）<br />\n會盡量每日更新<br />\n另附上食環舉報熱線 2868 0000或 1823 <br />\n<br />\nenquiries@fehd.gov.hk<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/comments/contact_us.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fehd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fcomments%2Fcontact_us.html&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRvsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=46b3e676\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/comments/contact_us.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撐黑警/撐送中黑店名單</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Ak4Hw9c01cfi_RAlMxI4PSiMK2H2WO9vJtmFd2hdwx0/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1Ak4Hw9c01cfi_RAlMxI4PSiMK2H2WO9vJtmFd2hdwx0%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRvsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=5d8612da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Ak4Hw9c01cfi_RAlMxI4PSiMK2H2WO9vJtmFd2hdwx0/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Facebook page</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JiJqJK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JiJqJK&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRvsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=383a3fab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JiJqJK</a><br />\n<br />\n補充表格<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/iRy1HizFPhpaGNt38\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FiRy1HizFPhpaGNt38&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRvsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=b6aa0927\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/iRy1HizFPhpaGNt38</a>"},{"pid":"42ceed26e